com.google.common.annotations
Annotation Type NonFinalForGwt

@Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value=FIELD)
@Documented
@GwtCompatible
public @interface NonFinalForGwt

Marks a field that normally would be final, but for GWT serializability purposes is not.

See GWT Serializable Types and the GWT issue about removing the non-final constraint.

Author:
Charles Fry
